700466f-a.text:
1673 to 1649 Barnes Ave. (left), west side, south from Van Nest to Baker Aves. On the south side of Baker Ave. is partly visible the repair shop of the New York, New Haven and Hartford Railroad. Also shown (extreme right) is No. 790 Van Nest Ave.

July 28, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
